Pondy Oxides & Chemicals Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 16/05/2025 inter alia to consider and approve (a) Audited Standalone and Consolidated Financial Statements for the financial year ended 2024-2025 and for the quarter ended 31st March 2025;
(b) Recommendation of final dividend if any for the financial year 2024-25;
(c) any other subject.
